36995>>>>>>>    Procedure Creating
36997>>>>>>>        DateTime dtCurrentDateTime
36997>>>>>>>        
36997>>>>>>>        Forward Send Creating
36999>>>>>>>        
36999>>>>>>>        //  Init usecounter
36999>>>>>>>        Move 0 to WebAppSession.UseCount
37000>>>>>>>        
37000>>>>>>>        //  Set the creation and access time to the current time
37000>>>>>>>        Move (CurrentDateTime()) to dtCurrentDateTime
37001>>>>>>>    
37001>>>>>>>        Get TimeToString dtCurrentDateTime to WebAppSession.CreateTime
37002>>>>>>>        Get TimeToString dtCurrentDateTime to WebAppSession.LastAccessTime
