37291>>>>>>>Class cPasswordHasher is a cObject
37292>>>>>>>    
37292>>>>>>>    Import_Class_Protocol cPasswordHasher_Mixin
37293>>>>>>>    
37293>>>>>>>    Procedure Construct_Object
37295>>>>>>>        Forward Send Construct_Object
37297>>>>>>>        
37297>>>>>>>        Property UInteger   peAlgorithm         C_PWH_PBKDF2_HMAC_SHA_512 
37298>>>>>>>        Property UInteger   puiSaltSize         16
37299>>>>>>>        
37299>>>>>>>        Property UInteger   puiOptTimeCost      420000
37300>>>>>>>    End_Procedure
37301>>>>>>>    
37301>>>>>>>    Function CreatePasswordHash String sPassword String ByRef sHash Returns Boolean
37303>>>>>>>        Boolean bOk
37303>>>>>>>        UInteger uiAlgo
37303>>>>>>>        Get peAlgorithm to uiAlgo
37304>>>>>>>        
37304>>>>>>>        Case Begin
37304>>>>>>>            Case (uiAlgo = C_PWH_PBKDF2_HMAC_SHA_256)
37306>>>>>>>            Case (uiAlgo = C_PWH_PBKDF2_HMAC_SHA_512)
37309>>>>>>>                Get CreatePasswordHashEx uiAlgo (puiSaltSize(Self)) sPassword (&sHash) (puiOptTimeCost(Self)) to bOk
37310>>>>>>>                Case Break
37311>>>>>>>            Case Else
37311>>>>>>>                Error 8710 "Invalid algorithm selected."
37312>>>>>>>>
37312>>>>>>>                Function_Return False
37313>>>>>>>        Case End
37313>>>>>>>        
37313>>>>>>>        Function_Return bOk
