37315>>>>>>>    
37315>>>>>>>    Function RequiredBufferSize Returns UBigInt
37317>>>>>>>        UBigInt ullSize
37317>>>>>>>        UInteger uiAlgo
37317>>>>>>>        Get peAlgorithm to uiAlgo
37318>>>>>>>        
37318>>>>>>>        Case Begin
37318>>>>>>>            Case (uiAlgo = C_PWH_PBKDF2_HMAC_SHA_256)
37320>>>>>>>            Case (uiAlgo = C_PWH_PBKDF2_HMAC_SHA_512)
37323>>>>>>>                Get RequiredBufferSizeEx uiAlgo (puiSaltSize(Self)) (puiOptTimeCost(Self)) to ullSize
37324>>>>>>>                Case Break
37325>>>>>>>            Case Else
37325>>>>>>>                Error 8710 "Invalid algorithm selected."
37326>>>>>>>>
37326>>>>>>>                Function_Return 0
37327>>>>>>>        Case End
37327>>>>>>>        
37327>>>>>>>        Function_Return ullSize
37328>>>>>>>    End_Function
37329>>>>>>>
37329>>>>>>>End_Class
