37503>>>>>        Set Field_Changed_Value of hoUserDD Field WebAppUser.LoginName to sLoginName
37504>>>>>        If (not(CreatePasswordHash(Self, Trim(sPassword), &sPassword))) Begin
37506>>>>>            Send Clear of hoUserDD
37507>>>>>            Function_Return False
37508>>>>>        End
37508>>>>>>
37508>>>>>        Set Field_Changed_Value of hoUserDD Field WebAppUser.Password to sPassword
37509>>>>>        Get Request_Validate of hoUserDD to iErr
37510>>>>>        If (iErr) Begin
37512>>>>>            Send Clear of hoUserDD
