37597>>>>>    
37597>>>>>    //
37597>>>>>    // This procedure is called when validating a session and after logging in. Its purpose is to 
37597>>>>>    // update properties based on the session and user data. Augment this function to update 
37597>>>>>    // properties based on the session / user table. Note that WebAppUser and WebAppSession contain
37597>>>>>    // the right records when this procedure is called.
37597>>>>>    //
37597>>>>>    // Params:
37597>>>>>    //      bClear   True if the procedure is called before session validation to clear properties.
37597>>>>>    //
37597>>>>>    Procedure UpdateSessionProperties Boolean bClear
37599>>>>>        Handle hoUserDD
37599>>>>>        
37599>>>>>        Get phoUserDD to hoUserDD
37600>>>>>        
37600>>>>>        //  Update user properties
37600>>>>>        If (not(bClear) and HasRecord(hoUserDD)) Begin
37602>>>>>            Set psUsername      to (Trim(WebAppUser.FullName))
37603>>>>>            Set psLoginName     to (Trim(WebAppUser.LoginName))
37604>>>>>            Set piTenantID      to webappuser.TenantID
37605>>>>>            Set piUserRights    to WebAppUser.Rights
37606>>>>>            
37606>>>>>            Send OnSessionPropertiesSet 
37607>>>>>        End
37607>>>>>>
37607>>>>>        Else Begin
37608>>>>>            Set psUsername      to ""
37609>>>>>            Set psLoginName     to ""
37610>>>>>            Set piTenantID      to 0
37611>>>>>            Set piUserRights    to 0
37612>>>>>            
37612>>>>>            Send OnSessionPropertiesClear
37613>>>>>        End
37613>>>>>>
37613>>>>>    End_Procedure
37614>>>>>    
37614>>>>>    Procedure OnSessionPropertiesSet
37616>>>>>        //  Empty event stub
37616>>>>>    End_Procedure
37617>>>>>    
37617>>>>>    Procedure OnSessionPropertiesClear
37619>>>>>        //  Empty event stub
37619>>>>>    End_Procedure
37620>>>>>    
37620>>>>>    Procedure EndSession
37622>>>>>        Integer iErr
37622>>>>>        Boolean bLogWebSession
37622>>>>>        Handle hoSessionDD       
37622>>>>>        
37622>>>>>        Get phoSessionDD to hoSessionDD
37623>>>>>        Get pbLogWebSession to bLogWebSession
37624>>>>>        If not bLogWebSession Begin
37626>>>>>            Forward Send EndSession
37628>>>>>            Procedure_Return
37629>>>>>        End
37629>>>>>>
37629>>>>>            
37629>>>>>        //  Check if session exists
37629>>>>>        Send Clear of hoSessionDD
37630>>>>>        Get psSessionKey to WebAppSession.SessionKey
37631>>>>>        
37631>>>>>        Send Find of hoSessionDD EQ Index.1
37632>>>>>        If (Found) Begin
37634>>>>>            Set Field_Changed_Value of hoSessionDD Field WebAppSession.Active to "N"
37635>>>>>            Get Request_Validate of hoSessionDD to iErr
37636>>>>>            If (iErr) Begin
37638>>>>>                // this should not happen. If it does its a programming error
37638>>>>>                Error DFERR_PROGRAM C_$WebAppSessionValidateFailed
37639>>>>>>
37639>>>>>                Procedure_Return
37640>>>>>            End
37640>>>>>>
37640>>>>>            Send Request_Save of hoSessionDD
37641>>>>>        End
37641>>>>>>
37641>>>>>    End_Procedure
