37741>>>    Procedure DoLogin
37744>>>        String  sLoginName sPassword sPrevStateHash
37744>>>        Integer iTenant
37744>>>        Boolean bResult
37744>>>        
37744>>>        WebGet psValue of oLoginName    to sLoginName
37745>>>        WebGet psValue of oTenant       to iTenant
37746>>>        WebGet psValue of oPassword     to sPassword
37747>>>        
37747>>>        Get UserLogin of ghoWebSessionManager sLoginName iTenant sPassword to bResult
37748>>>        
37748>>>        If (bResult) Begin
37750>>>            Send Hide of oLogin
37751>>>            Send ShowHeader of ghoWebApp
37752>>>            WebSet psCSSClass of ghoWebApp to ""
37753>>>            
37753>>>            WebGet psPrevStateHash to sPrevStateHash
37754>>>            Send NavigateToStateHash of ghoWebApp sPrevStateHash True
37755>>>            
37755>>>            // clear the login values. we don't want to return the login id & password as synchronized properties....
37755>>>            WebSet psValue of oLoginName to ""
37756>>>            WebSet psValue of oPassword  to ""
37757>>>            WebSet psValue of oTenant    to ""
37758>>>            WebSet pbVisible of oWarning to False
37759>>>        End
37759>>>>
37759>>>        Else Begin
37760>>>            WebSet pbVisible of oWarning to True
37761>>>        End
37761>>>>
37761>>>    End_Procedure
