40573>>>
40573>>>        // if this view is being used in multiple contexts, you may need a block of code
40573>>>        // like this to handle customizations. This would include hiding rows and buttons
40573>>>        // (WebSet pbRender) and changing the values of various captions.
40573>>>        Case Begin
40573>>>            Case (NavigateData.eNavigateType = nfFromMain)
40575>>>                // If from main, this is a probably a main file Select to Zoom.
40575>>>                // This is the most typical way to navigate to a zoom.
